rom\": 1149, \"to\": 1159}, {\"ngram\": \"her hometown\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She admitted seeing Olympic counterparts collect lucrative incentives fromWorld Athleticsfor similar achievements to hers was \\\"frustrating\\\".\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1382, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic counterparts\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1282}, {\"ngram\": \"lucrative incentives\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"Athleticsfor similar achievements\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really lucky, this Games I have some incredible sponsors behind me who are giving me medal bonuses, it's the first time ever that I will have sponsor medal bonuses, so it's a massive step forward,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some incredible sponsors\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"medal bonuses\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1509}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsor\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"medal bonuses\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1553}, {\"ngram\": \"a massive step\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not thousands but it's money.\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But yeah, it's tough seeing the Olympic guys get the money from World Athletics and then we can not replicate, it's frustrating.\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1699, \"end\": 1714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9990147261757932, \"rank\": 0.0009862455463010966, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/